snippet.title: LIVE: London court hears closing arguments of Johnny Depp's libel trial: stakeout
snippet.description:
Ruptly is live outside the High Court in London on Monday, July 27, as actor Johnny Depp and his ex-wife Amber Heard are expected to be present while the closing arguments in Depp’s libel trial against The Sun newspaper are made. 
 
Depp brought the lawsuit against the publication over a 2018 article claiming he was abusive to Heard. 
 
She has testified in defence of the publisher, speaking about the occasions in which she claims Depp attacked or threatened to kill her.
